                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/68" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0026</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8906 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连精睿节能技术服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dalian Kingree-energy Technology ＆ Service Co., Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曲伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连精睿节能技术服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">民营企业；节能服务；商业模式；游击营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Energy saving service; Business model; Guerrilla marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业不仅在中国，而且在全世界，正在以难以置信的速度发展。许多不同年龄、不同背景和生活处境的人，正在创办自己的企业，并重新构建着全球经济。正是那些来自创新企业规模的固有优势，诸如速度、灵活性、对顾客需求的敏感、创造力、创新精神和许多其它因素，使创新企业能够成功地与规模和预算数倍于自己的大公司竞争。然而，由于竞争环境的复杂多变，创业者自身又缺乏全局的战略管理思想、先进的经营理念和经营方法，同时受到各种外部环境和内部条件的制约，创业之路从来就不平坦。
本文采用案例文体，分为“案例正文”和“案例使用说明”两个部分。案件正文通过创业动机、创业机会识别、商业模式和营销四个方面的典型案例，描述了大连精睿节能技术服务有限公司经理方宇在创业过程中遇到的各种问题以及解决方式。案例使用说明则首先阐述了节能服务行业在大连市的发展现状，然后从创业者应该具备的基本素养和能力、创业机会的甄别方法、商业模式的选择以及小企业在竞争中应采取的营销战略，分析了当前的创业环境和从该企业的发展中可以得到的经验和教训。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Not only in China but also in whole world is the growing trend of entrepreneurial actions with unbelievable high speed. Now many people from different age groups, living background and environment are devoting themselves to entrepreneurial actions and rebuilding the construction of global economy. The  entrepreneurship-oriented enterprises have their unique strengths which may lie in working efficiency, flexibility, sensitiveness to the customers’ demand, innovation, entrepreneurial ability and many other factors. It was these strengths that the small enterprises depended on to compete with those giant companies whose scale and budget is larger by many times than theirs. Nevertheless, there will be no doubt that the road of entrepreneurial actions is unlikely to be flat because of the complexity of competing environment, the entrepreneur’s lack of strategic thought, advanced managing ideas and patterns, as well as various restrictions imposed by external and internal environment. 
This thesis is divided into two parts. The first part is the case details, through typical cases in four aspects, entrepreneurship motives, opportunity distinguishing business model and marketing, described the problem Dalian Kingree-energy Technology ＆ Servicing Co., Ltd. General Manager Fang Yu encountered during the process of establishing enterprise and the solutions. The second part is the case user instructions, through applying the related theory to dissect the emergence reason of the typical cases and solution to the problems.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2009</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业动机、创业机会、商业模式、营销战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011-04</td>
